{"tid":1555561,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[「我無嘢講，我要見律師」極有用短片, 點解得咁少view","createTime":"2019-09-09T11:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T16:40:45.000Z","uid":30274,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"1b37bea970f13371bf3410d9aa6f96e9e3f92c08","tid":1555561,"uid":30274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lawlaydream/videos/506960973456133/UzpfSTYyNTMzNDY2NzY0OTg4MzoxMTg1OTY0NTE4MjUzNTU5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flawlaydream%2Fvideos%2F506960973456133%2FUzpfSTYyNTMzNDY2NzY0OTg4MzoxMTg1OTY0NTE4MjUzNTU5%2F&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2Bumo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=19efd4f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lawlaydream/videos/506960973456133/UzpfSTYyNTMzNDY2NzY0OTg4MzoxMTg1OTY0NTE4MjUzNTU5/</a><br />\n<br />\n//【聯合轉載】<br />\n<br />\n「我無嘢講，我要見律師」呢句大家都聽到耳熟能詳，其實警察都係，佢地都識得進化。<br />\n<br />\n這條短片，是義工參考了被捕人士的真實經歷，顯示警察有多種方法去挑釁、濫權、以及擾亂被捕者。這短片未能窮盡所有情景，如果想了解更多被捕人士權利，可以參考法政匯思(<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MKdbpy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MKdbpy&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2Bumo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=d9a0b103\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MKdbpy</a>)<br />\n<br />\n無論如何，我地希望通過這條短片，讓大家知道，就算遇上任何情況，都要保持冷靜，盡量保護自己。 顯示較少"},{"pid":"058511fa2362b6ea375ea076320bdd29d9f24137","tid":1555561,"uid":40465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:39:01.000Z","msg":"知多啲保護自己"},{"pid":"b7334305014a582325fdb43b23d3e9cbe2d74a9d","tid":1555561,"uid":132625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:37:00.000Z","msg":"高質 <br />\n必推<br />\n<br />\n好多義士忘記咗<br />\n讓我哋溫故知新<br />\n<br />\n1/30"},{"pid":"38909c16bee96a9d87ea8fe808a093fc6cdb21c8","tid":1555561,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:37:44.000Z","msg":"2/30"},{"pid":"123dd7a43f4cfcc3356a4f717cd046a811a6c1e0","tid":15